Class Board

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.Board

  • public class Board
extends java.lang.Object
    Board class. Holds a 2D array of all the current tiles. These tiles contain information about the board, such as where Chap is.
